---
title: Carb Smart Dilly Bacon Ranch Salad  with Jammy Eggs and Fried Capers
description: Crisp, smoky bacon and salty capers make a perfect duo in this simple and satisfying salad, complete with hearty hard-boiled eggs!

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

